      "content": "i rly dont have time to go to a doctor right now lol. i have a massive deadline this week and cant be sitting in a waiting room. can u just tell me if it's safe to try the drops first? like if i just use them a few times a day for a bit, is there any real risk if it actually turns out to be an infection?",
