    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u saying the drops could make the infection worse?? i thought they were just water based and harmless. if it's just a tiny bit of bacteria, wont the drops just wash it out? i really just want to know if i can just dose it heavily with the drops for a couple days to see if it clears up before i commit to a doctor visit. like how many times a day is usually fine?",
